Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:43.58,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'm saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:50.17,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'm not playing Touya Kouyou or\Nold man Kuwabara right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:53.84,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's just a new pro player.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.60,0:02:00.39,Thinking,,0,0,0,,And... isn't this Shindou's first\Ntime playing One-Color Go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.02,0:02:04.16,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Touya Akira isn't the only one...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:07.90,Thinking,,0,0,0,,who will be threatening me from below.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:11.40,Thinking,,0,0,0,,There is someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:16.82,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(315,115)}The Fifty-Ninth Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:16.82,Title_eps,,0,0,0,,{\fad(274,0)\q2\blur0.8\fscy70\fscx333\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\pos(325,365)}Touya Kouyou Retires!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.58,0:02:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya Meijin retired!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he doing this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.21,0:02:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He simply made a phone call apologizing to\Nme since I was the head of his supporters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We did arrange for a press conference,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but all he said was that it was\Nwhat he wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.85,0:02:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichikawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just as surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Anyway, we have to... umm...\Nhold an emergency meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.69,0:02:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... we have a phone call from\Nthe sponsor of a title match.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.78,0:02:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be because of his health?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try going to Kouyou's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not fair! It's too early!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I still haven't taken a title from Touya Meijin yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.84,0:03:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Being defeated in the Jyudan match has\Nnothing to do with his retirement.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.34,0:03:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had to retire just because you lost a title,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'd have to retire as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt as if I was playing against a whole new Touya\NKouyou in the last game of the Jyudan match.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So why retire?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.69,0:03:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen to the title matches\Nthat no longer have a current title holder?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Make the challenger the temporary title holder?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't we make the final match to decide\Nthe challenger a five or seven game match?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a rumor that Touya-san lost\Nto an amateur on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But boy was I surprised when\NI took a look at the Kifu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an incredible game!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That had to have been a match\Nbetween top-class pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:04:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So the rumor that he's retiring out of\Ndisappointment from losing to Sai is just a rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is too bad that we still don't\Nknow which pro player Sai is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, I'm going to be late for the\Nbullet train if I keep talking here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.57,0:04:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, my wife's family is\Nholding a memorial service,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, you're such a selfish man, Touya Kouyou.
