Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Touya Akira. Where is the match hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you there right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Touya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,About your father's retirement...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all worried here that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,it's because of his health.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No. His health is perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.07,0:04:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:04:59.65,Background,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:04.87,Background,,0,0,0,,We don't get very reliable information\Nhere or in the western district.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.37,0:05:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that even you don't know\Nhis reasons for retiring...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. My mother does not know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Mother said to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:22.18,Memory,,0,0,0,,Akira-san, there's no need to\Nworry about your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:27.77,Memory,,0,0,0,,I mean, he doesn't look at all as\Nif he's torn about this decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But wouldn't he miss being able to play Go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. Many players have already\Ncome to our house to play him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But... this is tragic news for Go fans!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let my father have his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make up for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The match hall is right upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,'I'll make up for him.'?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Make up for a pro with four titles?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He said it so casually. He's going\Nto grow up to become somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Touya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Ichiryuu... in Nagoya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Right back at you. There are hardly\Never matches here in Nagoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife’s family lives here in Nagoya,\NI'm here for a memorial.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought I'd come here to take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you stay at a hotel last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That must have been rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.68,0:06:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How is the former Meijin, Touya, doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's playing Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Mr. Morishita and Mr.\NOokubo have come to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Mr. Ookubo!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.48,0:06:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Kurata-kun went as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:06:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Ichiryuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Miyamachi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:06.32,Background,,0,0,0,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:09.24,Background,,0,0,0,,What is a person of your stature\Ndoing here, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:13.33,Background,,0,0,0,,I came to cheer you on! Why else would I be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:14.96,Background,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.34,Background,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:28.59,Background,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that you can play Go\Neven now that you're retired,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't quite agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, aren't there things that you can\Nonly see in the tension of a title match?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurata-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That is certainly true for you and Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many things you need\Nto learn through competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:53.16,Background,,0,0,0,,But in my case,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:56.71,Background,,0,0,0,,I'm happier about being freed\Nfrom meaningless obligations
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:08:03.38,Background,,0,0,0,,and matches in places that I have to\Nspend two days getting to and from.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So now, you can sit here, and people\Nwill come to you for games instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I did today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.15,0:08:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurata-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned a lot from you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll work hard to try to catch\Nup to you and Ogata-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have lost to you in the second\Npreliminaries for the Meijin match,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but I will grow stronger and\Nget even with you some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always looking up aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.18,0:08:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably don't realize that there's someone\Nthreatening below you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Below me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really below you... but immediately behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You and he are the people who are going\Nto be threatening me in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He just became a pro this year... Shindou Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably don't know him since\Nyou're always looking above.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.54,0:09:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I probably wouldn't have taken notice\Neither if I hadn't met him at a convention.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I played him once in a Go salon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:26.96,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's someone you have to watch out for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.01,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:41.14,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Even Kurata-san has noticed Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:45.11,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If only I wasn't playing in Nagoya...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:49.61,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I could have watched your match today in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:51.86,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:56.16,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs14\1c&H566265&\bord0\shad0\fscy120\frz345\pos(377,171)}Japanese Go Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:56.16,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\bord1.5\shad0.5\fs19\pos(318,365)}Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:10:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand how he can retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't he make a hundred million yen this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he won't have any financial problems...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's your opponent today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.47,0:10:14.18,Background,,0,0,0,,A newbie named Shindou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:18.01,Background,,0,0,0,,He had a win by default on his first\Nmatch, and today is his second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Win by default!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,His opponent, Touya Akira didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Touya collapsed that morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's his first time playing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be frozen stiff from nervousness then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:54.26,Thinking,,0,0,0,,When I checked up on his scores\Nfrom the Wakajishisen last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:56.76,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I saw that he lost to Murakami in the first round.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:11:00.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,And his new first dan series game was horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.81,0:11:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:06.35,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What's more, he should be frozen\Nstiff since it's his first match.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.98,0:11:10.02,Thinking,,0,0,0,,As a third dan, I can't afford to lose here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:23.37,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The 19x19 grid seems smaller than usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:27.00,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:29.38,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I feel like I can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:37.26,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru is starting to walk down\Nthe path to the divine move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.31,0:11:42.47,Sai,,0,0,0,,Not me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:44.14,Sai,,0,0,0,,but Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:54.86,Sai,,0,0,0,,Is there no way I can escape\Nthis fate God has for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:43.91,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It's a difficult game...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:48.87,Thinking,,0,0,0,,No, he's making it a difficult game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:55.13,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I have to change the flow... the flow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.18,0:13:02.22,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Change it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:11.73,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I spent too many moves on the upper side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:15.15,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Black's done well gaining territory while attacking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:20.07,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I have to make two eyes even\Nif I have to make weak moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:22.03,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I can only endure for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:25.08,Thinking,,0,0,0,,You can't just make eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:27.79,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'm going to gain a huge lead while you muck around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.01,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Not good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:05.99,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I did connect...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:11.16,Thinking,,0,0,0,,but in the meantime, he's invaded my area of influence,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:12.50,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I lost out...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:19.96,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The only place left where I can make\Na comeback is on the left side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:22.97,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I have to take a chance and attack it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:45.82,Sai,,0,0,0,,So this is Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.63,0:15:00.38,Sai,,0,0,0,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:05.05,Thinking,,0,0,0,,All he needed to do was defend
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.22,0:15:08.30,Thinking,,0,0,0,,against my reckless attack, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:11.81,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's retaliating instead of defending!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:14.39,Sai,,0,0,0,,I had no idea he had grown so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:37.58,Background,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Comment: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:38.21,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs14\1c&H241C56&\bord0\blur0\shad0\\alpha&H40&\fscy130\frz5\pos(600,100)}Japanese Go
Comment: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:42.34,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs14\1c&H241C56&\bord0\blur0\shad0\fscy130\\alpha&H40&\frz5\move(600,102,600,485)}Japanese Go
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:42.75,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs14\1c&H241C56&\bord0\blur0\shad0\\alpha&H40&\fscy130\frz5\move(600,100,600,520,57,4603)}Japanese Go
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:15:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:08.95,ed64_romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs21\1c&H000000&\shad0\bord0\blur0\frz25\pos(216,200)}Win by\NResignation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:08.95,ed64_romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs21\1c&H000000&\shad0\bord0\blur0\frz300\pos(532,249)}Naemura
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:08.95,ed64_romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs21\1c&H000000&\shad0\bord0\blur0\frz300\pos(480,277)}Aida
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:08.95,ed64_romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs21\1c&H000000&\shad0\bord0\blur0\frz300\pos(425,293)}Ishihara
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:08.95,ed64_romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs21\1c&H000000&\shad0\bord0\blur0\frz300\pos(378,320)}Touya
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:08.95,ed64_romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs21\1c&H000000&\shad0\bord0\blur0\frz300\pos(321,337)}Matsushima
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:08.95,ed64_romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs21\1c&H000000&\shad0\bord0\blur0\frz300\pos(273,365)}Tamura
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:08.95,ed64_romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs21\1c&H000000&\shad0\bord0\blur0\frz300\pos(208,381)}Horiguchi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:08.95,ed64_romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs21\1c&H000000&\shad0\bord0\blur0\frz300\pos(161,409)}Miyamoto
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:08.95,ed64_romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs21\1c&H000000&\shad0\bord0\blur0\frz300\pos(108,431)}Uehara
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:08.95,ed64_romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs21\1c&H000000&\shad0\bord0\blur0\frz300\pos(61.5,458)}Hon
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:12.91,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened in Shindou's game...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishihara-san, how was Touya Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:24.92,Background,,0,0,0,,No matter how much I study Go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:27.59,Background,,0,0,0,,I'll never beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:36.43,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking ever since the matter with Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:38.31,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:43.19,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Why did you appear before me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:46.57,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Why do I chase after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.74,0:16:49.99,Thinking,,0,0,0,,And why do you chase after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:53.91,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:16:59.37,Background,,0,0,0,,How was my match today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:02.33,Background,,0,0,0,,Wasn't I doing great?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He just wouldn't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,His persistence almost became annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet he thought he couldn't possibly lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.94,0:17:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:27.48,Sai,,0,0,0,,What is this move you just made!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:32.07,Sai,,0,0,0,,How can you be so arrogant when\Nyou make stupid moves like this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're right, this is a bad move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:40.87,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru can't even beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.59,0:17:48.01,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, you can't even beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.09,0:17:50.76,Ed5Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50\pos(280,300)\1aFF\2aFF\3aFF\4aFF\t(0,1979,\fs70)\t(0,750,\1a0\2a0\3a0\4a0)\t(1979,2670,\1aFF\2aFF\3aFF\4aFF\fs200}I want to play\Nmore Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:54.76,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yes! Hikaru can't even beat me yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.31,0:17:57.33,Ed5Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs30\pos(320,370)\1aFF\2aFF\3aFF\4aFF\t(0,1474,\fs40)\t(0,200,\1a0\2a0\3a0\4a0)\t(1474,2020,\1aFF\2aFF\3aFF\4aFF\fs200}I want an\Neternity of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.31,0:18:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can't even pick up Go stones without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... let's play...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:43.06,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru... let's play...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one that quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:49.07,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:53.57,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs14\1c&H090705&\bord0\shad0\frz36\pos(278,60)}The Hint to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:53.57,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs14\1c&H090705&\bord0\shad0\frz36\pos(290,69)}Tsumego
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he in such a bad mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:05.62,Background,,0,0,0,,Someone robbed Grandpa's storage shed!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He called just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They only took some of the things in the shed,\Nand both Grandpa and Grandma are fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:21.18,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru! The Go board... is the Go board alright!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:26.10,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The Go board that you lived in for a hundred forty years?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:27.06,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:31.40,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I thought it was disgusting because\Nthere were blood stains on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:35.20,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But it's a Go board filled with memories\Nof Torajirou for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.24,0:19:37.86,Sai,,0,0,0,,Let's go check! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:41.99,Thinking,,0,0,0,,And to think Sai was picking a\Nfight with me just last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:44.12,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:48.13,Background,,0,0,0,,Great! They didn't take the Go board.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:53.34,Background,,0,0,0,,It's not great at all! The pots, plates, and wall\Nscrolls... they took them all last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I'm glad that you came here\Nbecause you were worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:04.06,Background,,0,0,0,,Dad told me not to because it's all junk anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:07.35,Background,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.69,0:20:12.86,Background,,0,0,0,,Grandma is Grandma, she said it's a perfect\Nopportunity to finally clean out the shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:17.49,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.37,0:20:23.99,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Is it just me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:28.04,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The stains look more faded than they were last time.
