Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.77,0:23:03.71,Sai,,0,0,0,,Why? Why is it not me, but Hikaru, God?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.16,0:23:06.54,Sai,,0,0,0,,I'm going to disappear, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:08.83,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru will...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.72,0:23:12.14,Background,,0,0,0,,Shindou! Let me play Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.55,0:23:24.38,Sai,,0,0,0,,Sorry Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.38,0:23:26.05,Sai,,0,0,0,,I'll be going soon.
